<emphasis id="E9E97D23FF89FF8B6F8AFC25FB72FC60" box="[1158,1162,969,992]" pageId="22" pageNumber="347">.</emphasis>
Danesch, Orchidee 22: 117 (1971); they differ from 9 chiefly in being 15-25 cm high, in having both the inner and outer perianth-segments greenish and more or less undulate, and the labellum 10-12x9-11 mm, scarcely curved upwards and without or with an inconspicuous appendage
<emphasis id="E9E97D23FF89FF8B6EC7FBD4FA37FBCF" box="[1483,1487,1080,1103]" pageId="22" pageNumber="347">.</emphasis>
